{
  "stem": "833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I was playing the piano pretty soon in a way so that I could play with my mother, four-handed piano, and [? perform ?] Schubert and Haydn pieces so that we could make music together.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Music was part of life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you-- I cannot tell you what it was, because today, you have that eternal loudspeaker that is accompanying our life every day all the-- all the 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You cannot even listen to a stupid advertising without having something in the background going on, groaning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other day, I heard something that was too funny for words-- a-- a bass tuba accompanying an automobile sales pitch with-- with groaning-- completely senseless noises.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that was called music.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, it was not such an extremely outrageous idea at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Being a musician was part of society.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I can tell you, if-- if a kid went into the street car with a violin case, everybody looked approvingly at that kid-- not today.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I haven't seen any kids with violins, kids going to the street car.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was part of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, I grew up without any of the electronic medias.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no radio, no television, no gramophone recording, nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you wanted to have music, you have to make it yourself or you had to go to a concert or possibly to a church.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I know, sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they-- then when later on, when I, of course, studied seriously.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I studied seriously immediately, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I recorded a conversation with my father when I was about 10 or 11-- 11.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was during the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe it was 12.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, that is not-- it's rather immaterial.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
